Health doubt the seriousness of the problem untill they see
evidences presented to them.
</P>
<P>
''If higher government officials and that of mass media are
ignorant of the problem, how could we be able to prevent the abuse
of drug among the youth and drug trafficking,'' he asked.
</P>
<P>
This trend has resulted in the increasing of rate of the abuse
of drugs such as chat, cannabis, alcohol and even some other hard
drugs among the youth in the country, he stressed.
</P>
<P>
Today is the International Day Against Drug Abuse and Illicit
Trafficking. The theme of this year's observation is ''mobilizing
communities to prevent drug abuse''. enditem

