<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, June 26 (Xinhua) -- Sierra Leone's new military leader Major
Johnny Paul Koroma said on Wednesday that he is ready to let outsted
president Ahmed Tejan Kabbah return to the country, a report reaching
here said today.
</P>
<P>
Koromah, who toppled Kabbah in the May 25 coup, said in an address
to the nation that Kabbah could return as long as he stopped
