enlisting support from Sinn Fein, whose IRA allies have been
fighting to end British rule in Northern Ireland.
</P>
<P>
Speaking on the prospects of his minority government after his
appointment, Ahern said: "Many of the best governments in this
country have been minority governments".
</P>
<P>
The 45-year-old new Irish Prime Minister promised to build "a
sound, stable and productive government." 
