in the first quarter, which totaled 20 million marks (11.6 million
US dollars), with turnover reaching nearly 5 billion marks (2.9
billion dollars), up 8.5 percent.
</P>
<P>
In 1996, lufthansa's group turnover rose 4.8 percent to 20.9
billion marks (12.12 billion dollars), while operational earnings
dropped by 9.3 percent to 686 million marks (398 million dollars).
