<HEADLINE> China's Human Rights Group Concludes Visit to Spain </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, June 26 (Xinhua) -- A Chinese human rights delegation
today ended its five-day visit to Spain, the last leg of its
four-nation European tour, and left for home.
</P>
