<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 27 (Xinhua) -- The Tunnel Projects and Track
Transport Designing Institute of Shanghai, the first such
professional organization in China, was set up here Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The forerunner of this institute is the Shanghai Tunnel
Projects Designing Institute, which was set up 30 years ago. In
recent years, the group designed tunnels and track transport
facilities totaling a length of 200 km. Most of these projects are
in Shanghai, including the tunnel of Yan'an Road and the Number
One Subway of Shanghai.
</P>
<P>
