<DATE_TIME> 1997-06-27 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Xinhua Commentary: Make Alarm Bell A Reminder (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 27 (Xinhua) -- At the moment when the Hong Kong
handover ceremony starts at the Hong Kong Convention and
Exhibition Center on July 1, the sky over the motherland will be
resounded with the solemn sound of a bell in Jinghai Temple in
Nanjing where the humiliating "Treaty of Nanking" was drafted
century and a half ago.
</P>
<P>
The bell will sound 155 times to mark the end of 155-year
humiliation sustained by the Chinese people and remind the people
not to forget the past.
</P>
<P>
More than 100 years ago, Britain launched one of the world's
dirtest wars against China and occupied Hong Kong for its opium
trade. China's resumption of the exercise of its sovereignty over
Hong Kong, erasing the last traces of disgrace, means a victory of
justice and human progress.
</P>
<P>
The whole process of settling the Hong Kong issue -- from the
change of attitude on the British part from persisting in the
three unequal treaties to accepting China's plan and the many
events that occurred after 1989 -- involved a stern trial of
national strength. Just as Deng Xiaoping once said, the Hong Kong
issue can be settled mainly because China has developed to become
a strong and trustworthy country in the world.
</P>
<P>
The period from 1840 and 1949 is both a history of humiliation
in which the Chinese suffered untold sufferings from imperialist
aggression and a history of struggle against foreign aggression by
the Chinese people. During the period, from the burning of opium
by Lin Zexu, the battle against British invaders waged by the
people in Sanyuanli in suburban Guangzhou to the eight-year war of
resisting Japanese aggression and the war to resist US aggression
and aid Korea, countless sons and daughters of the Chinese nation
laid down their lives for safeguarding independence of the
motherland, the dignity of the nation and sovereignty of the state.
</P>
<P>
Sounding of the bell is exactly for the purpose of letting the
people engrave in their minds and carry forward the spirit of
sacrifice for the motherland and calling on the Chinese Communist
Party members to become exemplars of the nation and patriotism in
the new historical period.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
