<DOCNO> XIE19970627.0234 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-06-27 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Xinhua commentary: Make Alarm Bell A Reminder (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The world is in for a crucial historical period. While
multi-polarization is becoming an irresistible trend, hegemonism
and power politics still dominate the world.
</P>
<P>
China, still in the initial phase of socialism, is focusing on
economic development and carrying on with reform and opening up
while persisting in the four cardinal principles in line with Deng
Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics, thus greatly boosting its comprehensive national
strength.
</P>
<P>
Still, China is a developing country, falling far behind
developed countries in terms of economic strength. Facing the
reality that some people in the west have never given up their
attempt to contain China and overthrow China's socialism, it is a
long term task to ward off interference by all kinds of forces and
maintain Hong Kong's stability and prosperity after its returns
and it still requires arduous efforts to settle Macao issue and
Taiwan issue according to the principle of "peaceful reunification
and one country, two systems".
</P>
<P>
The sounding of the bell in Jinghai Temple is exactly for the
purpose of alerting the people to danger in time of peace,
stressing the necessity of education in patriotism and socialism
and the importance of enhancing the rallying power of the nation
and making the country powerful and strong by following Deng
Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics so as to make China always stand aloft among the
forest of nations in the world.
</P>
<P>
"it is a century's wish to make the country strong and the
people wealthy; the future is bright; may the great cause be
carried forward from generation to generation." This part of the
inscription on the bell in Jinghai Temple is very encouraging. Let
the bell always ring in our minds and encourage us to hold aloft
the great banner of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism
with Chinese characteristics, safeguard independence of the
nation, build a powerful and prosperous country and strengthen
friendship and cooperation with the people in the other parts of
the world so as to make our new constributions to building a just
and reasonable new international order and creating a more
beautiful world.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
