<HEADLINE> Minutes for Holyfield-Tyson Title Bout </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 26 (Xinhua) -- Following are the minutes for
the heavyweight title bout of the World Boxing Association between
champion Evander Holyfield and challenger Mike Tyson in Las Vegas
on Saturday:
</P>
<P>
Evander Holyfield  Mike Tyson
</P>
<P>
34 Age  30
</P>
<P>
218 lbs (99 kg)  Weight 218 lbs (99 kg)
</P>
<P>
6' 2.5" (1.89 m) Height 5' 11.5" (1.82 m)
</P>
